OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FRecent analysis by the AA Driving
OL,7,FSchool showed the average waiting time
OL,8,Fto book a practical test in Britain
OL,9,Fwas 20 weeks in February, up from 14
OL,10,Fweeks a year earlier. Why do learner
OL,11,Fdrivers have to wait so long to take a
OL,12,Ftest, and what plans have the
OL,13,Fgovernment unveiled in a bid to speed
OL,14,Fup the process?
