OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FThe pandemic had a huge impact on wait
OL,7,Ftimes after driving schools were
OL,8,Fforced to stop tests in compliance
OL,9,Fwith Covid lockdown rules, resulting
OL,10,Fin a big backlog.
OL,12,FBut five years on from the beginning
OL,13,Fof the pandemic, delays show few signs
OL,14,Fof improving.
OL,16,FThere are also suggestions that there
OL,17,Fis a higher demand for tests as
OL,18,Fgreater numbers of unprepared learner
OL,19,Fdrivers are having to retake them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
