OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FRecent data from the Driver and
OL,7,FVehicle Standards Agency revealed the
OL,8,Fnumber of tests passed fell this year,
OL,9,Fdown from 86,501 in March 2024 to
OL,10,F79,541 in March 2025.
OL,12,FDVSA encourage learner drivers not to
OL,13,Ftake their test until they can say
OL,14,F"yes" to five points.
OL,16,FSteve Gooding, director of motoring
OL,17,Fresearch charity the RAC Foundation,
OL,18,Fsaid "the best way candidates can help
OL,19,Fthemselves is to be as prepared as
OL,20,Fpossible for test day".
