OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,F"At the moment less than 50% of tests
OL,7,Ftaken are passed," he said.
OL,9,FThe test backlog was further strained
OL,10,Fby industrial action at the Driver and
OL,11,FVehicle Standards Agency.
OL,13,FIn 2024 members of the PCS Union took
OL,14,Faction over pay, and plans to expedite
OL,15,Fdriving tests, which workers said
OL,16,Fcould impact safety and the ability to
OL,17,Fmaintain high standards.
OL,19,FThe four-day strike affected 270 test
OL,20,Fcentres across the UK and led to
OL,21,Fcancelled tests and further delays.
