OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FThere has also been a rise in
OL,7,Fautomated bots exploiting the system.
OL,8,FOrganisations are using bots to find
OL,9,Fand secure available slots more
OL,10,Fquickly than individual customers.
OL,11,FThey then resell these slots at a
OL,12,Fhigher price. This means that those
OL,13,Fwho are ready to take their test can
OL,14,Fstruggle to find one at a date and
OL,15,Ftime of their choice.
