OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FWhat is being done about it?
OL,8,FThe government has outlined plans to
OL,9,Fadd 10,000 extra driving tests a month
OL,10,Fin a bid to clear the backlogs.
OL,12,FThe Transport Secretary, Heidi
OL,13,FAlexander, told the Commons' Transport
OL,14,FSelect Committee that her department
OL,15,Fis aiming to reduce the average
OL,16,Fwaiting time for driving tests in
OL,17,FBritain to seven weeks by summer 2026.
