OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FThe government has also announced
OL,7,Fplans to double the number of driving
OL,8,Ftest trainers to skill up new
OL,9,Fexaminers quickly and ask qualified
OL,10,Fexaminers to return to the frontline
OL,11,Fto provide practical tests.
OL,13,FFurthermore, they are accelerating the
OL,14,Finvestigation into the potential abuse
OL,15,Fof the test booking system by bots.
OL,17,FThe DVSA are playing their part as
OL,18,Fwell, in December 2024 launching a
OL,19,Fseven-point plan to cut waiting times.
