OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FMeasures included recruiting and
OL,7,Ftraining 450 new examiners and
OL,8,Fimproving the test booking system,
OL,9,Fwith proposed legal changes if
OL,10,Frequired.
OL,12,FThe changes would see stricter terms
OL,13,Ffor instructors using booking services
OL,14,Fto prevent misuse, as well tougher
OL,15,Fpenalties for candidates who miss or
OL,16,Fdisrupt tests.
OL,18,FAdditionally, the 'Ready to Pass?'
OL,19,Fcampaign will help learners prepare
OL,20,Fmore effectively by promoting skills,
OL,21,Fmock tests, and readiness assessments.
