OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the rules around
OL,7,Fcancelling driving tests were also
OL,8,Fchanged.
OL,10,FFrom April 8, learner drivers have had
OL,11,Fto give at least 10 working days
OL,12,Fnotice to cancel their test or lose
OL,13,Fthe test fee, prior to this it was
OL,14,Fonly three days.
OL,16,FThe change aims to avoid test slots
OL,17,Fbeing wasted.
