OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FWith these measures in mind, the
OL,7,Fgovernment aims to reduce driving test
OL,8,Fwaiting times to 7-weeks by Summer
OL,9,Fnext year.
OL,11,FWill this make any difference?
OL,13,FIt's hard to say. The latest test data
OL,14,Fshows that wait times have hit a new
OL,15,Fhigh with the number of tests being
OL,16,Fconducted falling substantially.
OL,18,FIn March 2025, a total of 162,259
OL,19,Ftests were conducted, around 12% fewer
OL,20,Fthan the previous year.
