OL,3,CWhy is it so hard to book a driving
OL,4,Ctest?
OL,6,FAccording to the DVSA already this
OL,7,Fyear, there have been around 583,000
OL,8,Ftests scheduled across the UK.
OL,10,FThe outlook last year looked bleak. In
OL,11,F2024, the car insurance company
OL,12,FMarmalade found that demand for
OL,13,Fdriving tests outweighed supply.
OL,15,FIt estimated that 3 million learners
OL,16,Fstruggled to get a test, with the DVSA
OL,17,Fonly able to accommodate an average of
OL,18,F170,248 per month, leaving a huge
OL,19,Frollover for 2025.
